Atomic consistency, asynchronous communication, orchestrated coordination

adding asynchrocity to orchestrated workflows adds asynchronous transactional state: race conditions, deadlocks etc.

Isn't a very good pattern

Qualities
    Communication               Asynchronous
    Consistency                 Atomic
    Coordination                Orchestrated
    Coupling                    High
    Complexity                  High
    Responsiveness/availability Low
    Scale/elasticity            Low